        "id": 2419
      },
      "writtenOn": "2015-02-27T13:43:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Looking at how we describe this elsewhere in the document we use the following description.\n\ndimensions ({string(255): string(255)}, optional) - A dictionary consisting of (key, value) pairs used to uniquely identify a metric.\n\nI think we should use something that is consistent a well as define the max length.",
      "revId": "7fe5df2e1b6aeeee05381d55ebcc0580e3dcb2f3",
      "serverId": "4a232e18-c5a9-48ee-94c0-e04e7cca6543",
      "unresolved": false
    },
